{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be secure and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Secure Law Firm</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #e0eaf2; /* Light Blue-Gray */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #0056b3 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            padding: 0 15px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8));\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%23e0eaf2\" fill-opacity=\"0.3\" d=\"M0,192L80,213.3C160,235,320,256,480,245.3C640,235,800,192,960,165.3C1120,139,1280,128,1360,122.7L1440,117L1440,320L1360,320C1280,320,1120,320,960,320C800,320,640,320,480,320C320,320,160,320,80,320L0,320Z\"></path></svg>');\n            background-repeat: no-repeat;\n            background-position: bottom;\n            background-size: cover;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #e0eaf2;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h3, #about h3, #contact h3 {\n            font-size: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        #services h3::after, #about h3::after, #contact h3::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 50%;\n            height: 3px;\n            bottom: -10px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 22px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p, .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 17px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n            gap: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Ensures padding doesn't affect width */\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            resize: vertical;\n            min-height: 120px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            grid-column: 1 / -1; /* Span across all columns */\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #004080;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        .security-note {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #888888;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Law Firm Name]</h1>\n            <p>Dedicated to Justice and Security</p>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n                <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container hero-content\">\n            <h2>Your Trusted Legal Partners</h2>\n            <p>Providing secure and reliable legal solutions for individuals and businesses.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Us</h3>\n            <p style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: auto; font-size: 18px;\">\n                [Law Firm Name] is a distinguished legal practice committed to upholding the highest standards of integrity, professionalism, and client confidentiality. We leverage our extensive experience and deep understanding of legal principles to provide robust and secure representation. Our firm prioritizes the protection of your interests through meticulous preparation and strategic legal counsel.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Services</h3>\n            <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Corporate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business regulations with secure strategies.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Litigation</h4>\n                    <p>Aggressive representation in court, safeguarding your rights.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Intellectual Property</h4>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Real Estate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Securing your property transactions and disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Family Law</h4>\n                    <p>Compassionate guidance through sensitive personal matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Cybersecurity & Data Privacy</h4>\n                    <p>Advising on legal compliance for digital security.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\" style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Legal Avenue, Justice City, JC 45678</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@[lawfirmname].com</p>\n            </div>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\" action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"subject\">Subject:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"subject\" name=\"subject\">\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n            <p class=\"security-note\">\n                Please note: Sending an email through this form does not create an attorney-client relationship. Do not send sensitive or confidential information via this form until an attorney-client relationship has been established.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Law Firm Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Secure Legal Representation | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for potential future enhancements (e.g., smooth scrolling)\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}